   MISSOURI-POLITICS (St. Louis) _ A congressional race in St.
Louis is being eagerly watched because it could affect how the
lines of Missouri's congressional districts are redrawn next year.
It's also racially charged, even though both leading candidates are
black. 900 words. By Jonathan Hicks.
