   CIT Group, $750 million of an intermediate global bond. Chase
H&AMP;Q.
</P>
<P>
   Duke Energy Field Services, $1.5 billion of debt securities in
two parts. Baa2/BBB/---. J.P. Morgan Securities and Merrill Lynch &AMP;
Co.
</P>
