baptisms across the country each summer as part of an annual
convocation ceremony in which congregants seek repentance and holy
renewal. By Nina Siegal.
</P>
<P>
   PHONE-TALKS (Undated) _ Developments in the contract dispute
between union telephone workers and Verizon Communications. Workers
walked off the job Sunday, replaced by managers, but negotiators
were continuing to talk. By Simon Romero.
