<P>
   GORE'S-WHIZKID (Los Angeles) _ The author of presidential
candidate Al Gore's Democratic party platform is Andrei Cherny, a
24-year-old wunderkind from the San Fernando Valley who worked on
his first presidential campaign while in eighth grade. By Alexa
Haussler. (Will move in the ``a'' national and ``n'' California
news files.)
