<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-06 19:47 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4153 &Cx1f; tad-z
u l BC-SCHOOL-QUIZ0807-COX     08-06 1264
